  -- `<C-h>`: Select split (`actions.select_split`)
  -- `<C-t>`: Select tab (`actions.select_tab`)
  -- `<C-p>`: Preview (`actions.preview`)
  -- `<C-c>`: Close (`actions.close`)
  -- `<C-l>`: Refresh (`actions.refresh`)
